text: Gaoussou Diakité (born 26 September 2005) is a Malian footballer. He plays as forward for FC Liefering in the Austrian 2nd league on loan from FC Red Bull Salzburg. ==Career == Diakité started his career at Guidars FC in Mali. In January 2024 he moved to Austria to FC Red Bull Salzburg.Homepage FC Red Bull Salzburg In Salzburg he was loaned to FC Liefering. On 2 March 2024 he made his debut for Liefering in the 2nd league. He came in as a substitute for Oliver Lukic against SKN St. Pölten.FC Salzburg Wiki ==References == Category:2005 births Category:Living people Category:Malian footballers Category:Association football forwards Category:FC Liefering players
